                           GAME HINTS AND TIPS

Typed in by PARASITE of LSD.

NOTE: If you are using a cracked version of a game listed below, a cheat
may not work, don't blame ume. Or it may just be a differant version!


MONTY PYTHON'S FLYING CIRCUS
When you get onto the high score table, enter your name as 'SEMPRINI'. When
you start the game, the options menu will now have the option of making the
hidden bonuses invisible or visible. When you die, you will start the game
on the last level you were on.

BACK TO THE FUTURE 2
When the game starts, press pause, and type 'THE ONLY NEAT THING TO DO'
(with spaces) for infinate lives.

STORMLORD
Type 'DRAGONBRIDGE' on the credits screen. A scrolltext will now say 'YOU
CHEATING SWINE'. Restart the game, press <SPACE> to pause, then press <L>
to skip levels.

ROBOCOP
When the game starts type 'BEST KEPT SECRET' for infinite lives.

STRYX
Press <HELP> and <M> at the same time to replenish energy.

ASTRO MARINE CORPS
Press <F6> and type any of the following level codes:
NOSTROMO
DISCOVERY
ENTERPRISE
DAGOBAN
REPLICANT
KRULL
METROPOLIS

RAINBOW ISLANDS
Type these on the title screen;
'BLRBJSBJ' for fast boots.
'RJSBJSBR' for double rainbows.
'SSSLLRRS' for First hint.
'LJLSLBLS' for second hint.
'LBSJRWL' for continue on all rounds.

To reach the secret room on each level, you must collect the diamonds in
this order; RED, ORANGE, YELLOW, GREEN, LIGHT BLUE, DARK BLUE, and MAUVE.
On the fifth island you'll find a box in the secret room which you should
collect. There's also a gate with a '7' on it, leading to island 7.

ROTOR
To get all the differant missions type 'GAG', 'SLY', or 'AWE' at any time.

FIGHTING SOCCER
This is a bug! A goal is awarded when your shot hits the post, providing
you shoot diagonally at it in a one player game, and directly at it in a
two player game!

RALLY CROSS
When you reach the track called LOCOMOTION, drive your car up the railway
track to the end. the race will finish, and you'll be awarded lots of extra
points!

FORGOTTEN WORLDS
On the title screen, type 'ARC' and press the <HELP> key to start. Now
pressing <L> will take you to the next level, and pressing <S> will take
you to the shop.

KLAX
Start the game as normal, and on the first wave press <CAPS LOCK> and then
hold down <SPACE> and press <3> to skip a level, or <4> to start on level
100!

CRACKDOWN
Start the game as usual and type 'SMURF', now pressing <F1> will give player
one infinate lives, and <F2> will give player two the same.

MANCHESTER UNITED
Press the left mousebutton and the game thinks another player has started,
and the opponents will freeze, making winning easy!

SHINOBI
Press pause, and type 'LARSXVIII' for infinite credits.

E-MOTION
type 'MOON UNIT' and press <F1> to advance a level, <F2> go back a level,
<F3> to advance 10 levels, and <F4> go back 10 levels.

GALAXY FORCE 2
On the title screen, or during play type 'DONKEY', <F3> takes you to the
end of the level.

GHOSTBUSTERS 2
Turn your AMIGA on, wait for the hand to appear, insert disk TWO, the hand
will disappear, and then come back, now insert disk one. During gameplay
press <ENTER> on the numeric keypad to advance a level.

X-OUT
Insert the disk, and hold both mousebuttons until the title screen appears.
When youre in the shop hold down <HELP> and <DEL> for a few seconds, now
choose your ships as normal, but you have infinite energy.
To get more cash at the beginning of th game, select the smallest ship
(the one at the top), then the weediest laser (the orange one with
single beam), and place it on the shopkeepers nose. Hit the fire
button to get the cash boost!

KID GLOVES
Pause the game, and type 'RHIANNON' followed by <F9>, if the game doesn't
unpause itself, restart and repeat the procedure. This will make you
invincible. I'm told the other <Fn> keys also do something, but i don't
know what.

NINJA SPIRIT
Type 'NO HUNS AT HAMPDEN AND NO SKOL AT IBROX', then press keys <0> - <9>
to select that level.
Pause the game, and press <CAPS>, then <CTRL>, then <SHIFT>, restart the
game, with infinate lives and no collision detection.

IVANHOE
Pause the game and type 'ZOBINETTE' and press <RETURN>, unpause and press
<,> for an extra life, and <N> to skip to the next level.

EYE OF HORUS
Type 'SPAM'  for infinate lives, and to use all the elevators!

SKIDZ
Press fire and hold down <ALT>, and tap <C> for infinite energy, or <M> to
skip a level.

SHADOW WARRIORS
In the intro hold down the following keys, <CTRL>, <J>, <ESC>, <5>, <F2>,
<RIGHT ALT>, <(>, <KEYPAD ENTER>, <HELP>. (You will need some help with
this.) The border will flash purple, and pressing <HELP> during the game
will advance you a level, and <Q> makes you invincible.
Start a two player game by pressing <1> and <2> together, then pressing <1>
or <2> will give that player an extra life.
It also claims here that <HELP> will get you to the next level!

SIM CITY
Press <CAPS LOCK> and hild down the letters 'FUND' to add $10,000 to your
fund, but every fifth time triggers an earthquake.

SLAYER
Kill the end of level guardian on level one, and crash into it's dead body
for infinite lives.

VIKING CHILD
Hers's three passwords;
DENIS<E> (forest)
SHARKMAN (Labyrinth)
NYMHARSW (Desert)

SUPER HANG-ON
Get the highest score on the highscore table, and enter your name as 750J.
Simultaniously hold down <Z> and <T> while the screen changes, the cheat
mode screen will appear. When you start the game, the amiga key will
activate a gun to shoot other bikes!

DYNASTY WARS
Press <F2> on the title screen to skip a level.

GHOSTS AND GOBLINS
Play the game till you get a highscore, Instead of entering your name,
enter )!(, followed by the END option, when you restart, and you lose your
armour, your invincible, and have infinate lives.
Type 'DELBOY' on the title screen for infinite lives.

DRAGONS BREATH
Here's some spells,

INCREASE EYESIGHT (This alas increases health and strength, but reduces
your speed)
2 x RASGON      Grind and heat
2 x IGELE       Normal and heat
1 x ACRUS       Mix and heat

INCREASE SPEED
2 x RASGON      Grind and heat
2 x AROLIG      Normal and heat
1 x ACRUS       Mix and heat

INCREASE WISDOM (But reduces eyesight)
2 x RASGON      Grind and heat
2 x HALORUS     Cut and condense
1 x ACRUS       Mix and heat

INCREASE STRENGTH AND HEALTH
2 x RASCON      Grind and heat
2 x ULIN        Mix and heat
1 x ACRUS       Grind and condense

THE UNTOUCHABLES
Type in SOUTHAMPTON GAZETTE, the screen flashes to indicate the cheat
mode is active. Now you can press F10 to skip levels.

OPERATION THUNDERBOLT
Typing SPECCY MODE in the high score table brings on double the
enemies.
EDOM TAEHC gives infinate lives.
WIGAN NINJA gives infinate lives, and press F7 to skip levels.

TITAN
Heres the level codes.

10 H67JR1
20 1R7DCG
30 BG6W61
40 294JBH
