60 9LQHVU

SUPER CARS
Type RICH to start on level 1 with lods of money
Type ODIE to start on level 2 with the Vaug interceptor
Type BIGC to start on level 3 with the Parsec Turbo

If you are having trouble with the bank manager, try these phrases,

I could murder a curry!
Does the infuidlator work?
I ought to knock your lights out!
Too Much!
I think it's started raining!
How much!
I've got a cat called garfield etc etc...
Does it come with a guarantee?
How's the sub-frame?
Are you trying to rip me off?
Is it fitted with CAT?
Hey, I an paying cash!
This parrot is dead!
Make me a better deal.
I'm a lumberjack!

NOTE: if he mentions Monty Python or Garfield, always reply with the
relevant phrase.

BEACH VOLLEY
During play type DADDY BRACEY to activate the cheat mode, now pressing
F1 lets you skip levels.

DOGS OF WAR
At any time, type TIMBO, then press F5 to give invunerability.

INTERPHASE
At any time during flight type FENNY (Capital F, the reat in lower
case), to activate the cheat mode. You are now taken to a view mode
which allows you to cycle through all the aliens and objects in the
game. your mouse will make them rotate and zoom in and out. Press the
right button for the next image.

CABAL
During the game type SCHLIKA, and the border will flash, press F2 to
finish the level.

ROADBLASTERS
At the starting line type LAVILLASTRANGIATO, then press the following keys
as required.

0 - Remove special weapons
1 - Fit UZ cannon
2 - Fit cruise missiles
3 - Fit electro shields
4 - Fit nitro injectors
G - End game
F - Refil fuel
X - Spin the car

SPACE ACE
Start playing, and pause it, Type DODEMODEXTER, and sit back and watch the
cartoon!

SWITCHBLADE
When the word SWITCHBLADE has assembled, hold down key 1 - 5 and the fire
button until you appear on the level you selected.

HAMMERFIST
Play the game till you have a highscore, and enter your name as  TAEHC OT
TNAW I, when you restart, <F7> will skip one screen at a time.

DYTER-07
On the loading screen type GIBB or (GGIB), pressing <W> for extra
weaponary, <S> for extra shields

CHARIOTS OF WRATH
For infinate lives press the joystick forward instead of fire to start.

BATTLE VALLEY
Type ROGER MELLIE THE MAN ON THE TELE for infinate lives.

IMPOSSAMOLE
Type these names in on the highscore table.

COMMANDO - No time limit for weapons
HEINZ - Three power bars
ANNFRANK - Low energy topped up
OOCHOUCH - Walk on water without dying
JUGGLERS - ????

AFTER THE WAR
Part two's code is 101069

BEVERLY HILLS COP
On the difficulty select screen type MELLIE, to access all the differant
sub-games.

ROCK 'N ROLL
When the game starts type your name as RAINBOW ARTS.
Now pressing F1 - F8 gives differant pickups.
F9 increases the depth of the map.
F10 puts you on the next level
pressing 1 - 4 provides keys of differant colours

Try typing your name in as COUNRTY to activate the jukebox.

DENARIS
Press <Z> after the game selection, then plug the mouse into port 2 and
hold the right mouse button while the rest of the game loads.

P-47
type ZEBEBEE into the highscore table.
F1 gives extra lives
F2 gives Skip level

TURRICAN
Type BLUESMOBIL on the highscore table for 99 lives.

PIPEMANIA
If you fill the screen completely with pipes, you get a 50,000 point bonus.

NEBULUS
On the menu type HELLOIAMJMP, and f1 - f8 will select level start.

PREDATOR
Press f10 whilst playing for full energy.

End.
